4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive AI and Machine Learning Engineer bootcamp designed for beginners. Over 16 weeks, students will learn essential skills such as Python, SQL, and statistics, while creating predictive models using libraries like Pandas and Numpy. The course includes three classes a week with a maximum of 12 students to ensure personalized attention. Participants will engage in real-life case studies and cover topics including supervised and unsupervised learning algorithms.

Instructors feature experts with extensive industry experience. Certificates issued upon completion are recognized by various organizations. The program is available in English and Spanish. 

